# ============================================================================
# CATEGORIES BREAKDOWN
# ============================================================================
#
# Basic SELECT:         Q1
# Aggregation:          Q2
# Single Filter:        Q3, Q4, Q5
# Multi-Filter:         Q6, Q7
# Multiple Ingredients: Q8
# OPTIONAL:             Q9, Q10
# Complex Filtering:    Q11, Q12, Q13
# Relationships:        Q14
# Recommendations:      Q15
#
# FEATURES USED:
# - FILTER with comparison operators
# - CONTAINS for string matching
# - OPTIONAL for optional properties
# - COUNT, GROUP BY for aggregations
# - ORDER BY for sorting
# - LIMIT for pagination
# - Multiple property paths
# - Complex boolean expressions
#
# ============================================================================
